OL,3,CThree-year-old suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,FThe mother of a three-year-old boy
OL,8,Ffrom Cornwall says she felt "angry,
OL,9,Fdisgusted and sick" after he suffered
OL,10,Fvomiting and diarrhoea after playing
OL,11,Fon their local beach.
OL,13,FPauline Jones took young Finley to
OL,14,FWidemouth Bay on the north Cornish
OL,15,Fcoast in November last year.
OL,17,FLater that day Finley became ill - and
OL,18,Fa friend's child, who had also been on
OL,19,Fthe beach, had the same symptoms.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
