OL,3,CThree-year-old suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,FPauline said: "We hadn't been living
OL,8,Fhere that long. Myself and another
OL,9,Fneighbour, her little boy and my
OL,10,Flittle boy went down to the beach.
OL,12,F"The boys dug in the sand, they got
OL,13,Ftheir hands all mucky, and that
OL,14,Fevening he was really poorly in bed.
OL,16,F"We went to the doctors, they just
OL,17,Fsaid he had a bit of sickness and
OL,18,Fdiarrhoea which should pass within a
OL,19,Fcouple of days.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
