OL,3,CThree-year-old suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,F"But the little boy down the road also
OL,8,Fhad the same thing exactly the same
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,F"It just made me feel a bit sick to my
OL,12,Fstomach, thinking I'd let him play
OL,13,Faround in something that had been
OL,14,Fmaybe contaminated with effluent and
OL,15,FGod knows what else."
OL,17,FPauline says she wrote to her local MP
OL,18,Fand contacted .
