OL,3,CThree-year-old suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,F"It made me really angry. It does put
OL,8,Fme off a little bit, which is a bit
OL,9,Fsad.
OL,11,F"When we were down at the beach, there
OL,12,Fwere people swimming in the sea while
OL,13,Fthe discharge was happening, and I'm
OL,14,F100% sure they had no idea."
OL,16,FLast year, South West Water recorded
OL,17,F58,249 sewage spills across the region
OL,18,F- an increase of 54% from the previous
OL,19,Fyear.
