OL,7,FThe company says one reason for this
OL,8,Fis the persistent stormy weather - but
OL,9,Fcampaigners say this is not a good
OL,10,Fenough excuse.
OL,12,FKirsty Davies, from Surfers Against
OL,13,FSewage, said: "The water companies
OL,14,Fhave known about this for years.
OL,15,FThey've known there is climate change
OL,16,Fand an increase in extreme weather.
