OL,3,CThree-year-old suffered vomiting and
OL,4,Cdiarrhoea after 'sewage release' on
OL,5,Cbeach
OL,7,F"Water companies now need to invest
OL,8,Fand address these issues. They are
OL,9,Fcurrently planning their five-year
OL,10,Fbusiness plan. They've got an
OL,11,Fopportunity now to start progressing
OL,12,Fand making change."
OL,14,FLuke Pollard, Labour MP for Plymouth
OL,15,FSutton and Devonport, said: "We've got
OL,16,Fto get to grips with this because the
OL,17,Famount of raw human effluent being
OL,18,Fpumped into our natural environment is
OL,19,Foften utterly disgusting. That's why
OL,20,Fwe need stronger action than the
OL,21,FGovernment is taking today."
