OL,7,FEnvironment Agency director of water
OL,8,FHelen Wakeham said: "Whilst it is
OL,9,Fdisappointing that water companies
OL,10,Fhave reported an increase in sewage
OL,11,Fspills in 2023, it is sadly not
OL,12,Fsurprising.
OL,14,F"We are pleased to see record
OL,15,Finvestment from the water sector, but
OL,16,Fwe know it will take time for this to
OL,17,Fbe reflected in spill data ` it is a
OL,18,Fcomplex issue that won't be solved
OL,19,Fovernight.
