OL,7,F"No other country has the level of
OL,8,Fmonitoring we do, with 100 per cent of
OL,9,Fstorm overflows in England now fitted
OL,10,Fwith a monitor.
OL,12,F"We are better placed than ever before
OL,13,Fto hold water companies accountable `
OL,14,Fthanks to intelligence from our new
OL,15,Fwhistleblower portal, our plans to
OL,16,Fexpand our specialised workforce, new
OL,17,Fenforcement powers, increased water
OL,18,Fcompany inspections and new tools to
OL,19,Finform our enforcement work."
