OL,7,FWater Minister Robbie Moore said: "I
OL,8,Fhave been clear that sewage pollution
OL,9,Fin our waters is unacceptable, which
OL,10,Fis why in just the last few months we
OL,11,Fannounced a consultation to ban water
OL,12,Fbosses' bonuses when criminal breaches
OL,13,Fhave occurred, quadrupled company
OL,14,Finspections next year, fast-tracked
OL,15,F#180m investment to cut spills,
OL,16,Flaunched a whistleblowing portal for
OL,17,Fwater company workers to report
OL,18,Fbreaches, and will soon set out our
OL,19,Fplans to ban wet wipes containing
OL,20,Fplastic.
